title: 81: Chaw, Sir!
dc:creator: A.J. Hanenburg
description: You guys. It's spring. If you find yourself ready to take a walk, go on a journey, or otherwise just be outside, you're no different from anyone in the 1300s. In this episode, we'll journey with Chaucer and his buddies on their trip to Canterbury.

itunes:subtitle: Let's go on pilgrimages!
